U. S. ANTIMONY REPORTS PRODUCTION AND LOS JUAREZ  MILL TESTING


April 4, 2016. Thompson 
Falls, Montana. United States Antimony Corporation (�USAC�, NYSE 
MKT �UAMY�) reported preliminary Q1 2016 production as follows:





Product


Q1 2016


Q1 2015


 Change




